
Overview of noun sloth

The noun sloth has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. sloth, slothfulness -- (a disinclination to work or exert yourself)
2. sloth, tree sloth -- (any of several slow-moving arboreal mammals of South America and Central America; they hang from branches back downward and feed on leaves and fruits)
3. sloth, laziness, acedia -- (apathy and inactivity in the practice of virtue (personified as one of the deadly sins))
